      • BendersOptimizationData

        public BendersOptimizationData​(java.lang.Double[][] simplexTableau,
                               int[] paramaterNegativeIndices,
                               int[] yVariableIndices,
                               FPP.LinearOptimization.Model.benders.BendersMasterCoefficientType[] yTypes)
        Initializes input data for bender algorithm. Simplex tableau needs to be given in this way:
        {{1d, 2d, 0d, 0d, 2d}, restriction 1
        {1d, 0d, 0d, 0d, 50d}, restriction 2
        {0d, 0d, 1d, 0d, 80d}, restriction 3
        {0d, 0d, 3d, 10d, 0d}} function Last column of restrictions is result Last column of function is constant All restrictions have to be <= Function must be minimizer
